sentences: Frank Fontsere (born September 2, 1967), is a professional drummer from Marietta, Georgia.
He is known mostly for his work in rap/metal group, Stuck Mojo (1996–2000) and heavy metal group, Fozzy (1999–2005, 2009–2022).
